Everything lost
is meant to be found.

74
00:06:39,699 --> 00:06:41,428
Don't worry.

75
00:08:48,361 --> 00:08:50,955
It's unbelievable!

76
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:51,962
Whoo!

77
00:08:52,031 --> 00:08:53,259
Oh, my God.

78
00:08:53,332 --> 00:08:55,766
This is huge.

79
00:09:01,674 --> 00:09:04,370
Wonderful.

80
00:09:04,443 --> 00:09:08,209
Jimmy, this is wonderful.

81
00:09:08,314 --> 00:09:09,508
Do you see what I see?

82
00:09:09,582 --> 00:09:11,174
Oh, my God.

83
