is collapsing!

97
00:11:09,969 --> 00:11:12,199
Aftershock!

98
00:11:12,271 --> 00:11:14,432
I think that's
a sign to leave!

99
00:11:14,507 --> 00:11:15,997
Two minutes.

100
00:11:16,075 --> 00:11:16,175
