105
00:11:32,391 --> 00:11:33,289
You take those two.

106
00:11:33,426 --> 00:11:36,020
We have to hurry up!

107
00:11:36,095 --> 00:11:38,029
We've got to go.
We've got to go now! Come on!

108
00:11:38,097 --> 00:11:39,530
Okay.

109
00:11:42,968 --> 00:11:44,833
Lara!

110
