She's disorientated.

114
00:16:42,468 --> 00:16:43,992
That's normal after three days.

115
00:16:44,069 --> 00:16:46,503
Nice day for a dip?

116
00:16:48,774 --> 00:16:50,742
Gentlemen...

117
00:16:50,809 --> 00:16:53,369
there is an expression:

118
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:57,710
"It's not nice
to fool Mother Nature."

119
00:16:57,783 --> 00:17:00,479
Yet that is precisely
what I've been doing

120
00:17:00,552 --> 00:17:01,780
for some time now.

121
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:08,191
Whether it be sarin gas
for Mr. San...

122
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:09,955
improved typhoid

123
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:12,190
for Mr. Krev to use
in the Balkans...

124
00:17:12,264 --> 00:17:14,528
enhanced cholera
for Mr. Duvalier.

125
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:16,158
But...

126
00:17:16,235 --> 00:17:19,227
