of Ebola,

147
00:18:44,456 --> 00:18:46,253
deadliest disease known to man.

148
00:18:46,358 --> 00:18:48,986
Highly contagious.

149
00:18:50,529 --> 00:18:52,929
However...

150
00:18:52,998 --> 00:18:54,898
as with all known diseases,

151
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:58,960
there exist stockpiles
of antiserum in the West.

152
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:29,156
There is no antiserum

153
00:19:29,234 --> 00:19:31,395
for what I am offering you.

154
00:19:31,470 --> 00:19:33,097
No treatment.

155
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:34,230
No vaccine, no cure.

156
00:19:34,306 --> 00:19:36,137
The modern world has never seen

157
00:19:36,208 --> 00:19:38,199
anything like
what I've uncovered.

158
00:19:38,277 --> 00:19:39,403
