$1 00 million each,
if you please.

165
00:20:22,154 --> 00:20:23,280
Where's Chen Lo?

166
00:20:23,355 --> 00:20:26,119
He's got the orb,
but Ml6 is on to him.

167
00:20:26,191 --> 00:20:27,180
How?

168
00:20:27,259 --> 00:20:29,284
He doesn't know,
but rather than risk

169
00:20:29,361 --> 00:20:31,090
bringing it here,
he's waiting.

170
00:20:31,163 --> 00:20:33,290
I have just told
a cabin full of men

171
00:20:33,432 --> 00:20:34,865
about Pandora.

172
00:20:34,933 --> 00:20:36,594
The clock cannot be reset.

173
00:20:36,668 --> 00:20:39,466
Tell Chen Lo to bring
the orb to me at once.

174
00:20:56,822 --> 00:20:59,222
You'll find the killers!

175
00:20:59,291 --> 00:21:01,054
Don't take it out on me!

176
00:21:02,294 --> 00:21:03,955
Ya!

177
00:21:04,029 --> 00:21:05,553
Ya!

