00:43:19,830 --> 00:43:22,355
If I want double what
Reiss offered me?

536
00:43:22,433 --> 00:43:24,264
Is it here?

537
00:43:24,335 --> 00:43:25,267
It's worth a lot.

538
00:43:25,336 --> 00:43:26,860
Well, then, if you know that,

539
00:43:26,937 --> 00:43:28,234
you know Reiss
will also kill you

540
00:43:28,305 --> 00:43:29,567
the moment you give it to him.

541
00:43:29,640 --> 00:43:32,768
And your government will
guarantee my safety?

542
00:43:32,843 --> 00:43:33,969
No.

543
00:43:34,044 --> 00:43:36,706
But I will.

544
00:43:36,780 --> 00:43:39,874
That must hurt,
saying that to me.

545
00:43:39,950 --> 00:43:42,441
Take the offer.

546
00:43:50,394 --> 00:43:53,124
You presume to give me orders?

547
00:43:53,197 --> 00:43:55,961
Take the offer,
before it expires.

548
00:43:56,033 --> 00:43:57,557
No.

549
00:43:57,635 --> 00:43:59,796
Then I will have to force you.

550
